-- Golfer MclIroy May Play for Ireland, Irish Independent Says
-- B y   D a r a   D o y l e
-- 2013-04-24T06:16:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-24/golfer-mcliroy-may-play-for-ireland-irish-independent-says.html
 Northern Irish golfer Rory McIlroy
may have to play for Ireland in the 2016 Olympics, the Irish
Indepedent said, citing Peter Dawson, president of the
International Golf Federation. McIlroy may play for Ireland as
he’s already represented the country in golf’s World Cup, the
newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dara Doyle at 
 ddoyle1@bloomberg.net  